sequenceDiagram
    participant HR as HR System
    participant E as Entra ID
    participant CAE as App (Teams/SP)
    participant N as Network (Palo Alto)

    HR->>E: Status: Terminated
    E->>E: Disable Account
    E->>CAE: Revoke Session (CAE Signal)
    Note right of CAE: Immediate Session Termination
    E->>N: Update Quarantine DAG
    Note right of N: IP Blocked in <120s
